#!/usr/bin/env bash
# Run on production server (104.238.162.40):
#   cd /var/www/NPPC-Website && bash scripts/add_round9_more_post911_aim.sh
#
# Source clusters:
#   - Tarek Mehanna (Boston federal jury 2011) — 17.5 yrs federal for
#     translating al-Qaida media, widely considered a First Amendment case
#   - Newburgh Four (May 2009 FBI sting in Newburgh NY, 25-yr federal
#     sentences; 3 of 4 had sentences reduced to time served July 2023 by
#     U.S. District Judge Colleen McMahon, who called the FBI's role the
#     "real lead conspirator")
#   - Holy Land Foundation 5 (Dallas federal jury 2008) — material support
#     to Hamas via Palestinian zakat committees; 15-65 yr federal sentences
#   - American Indian Movement (Pine Ridge / RESMURS) — Dennis Banks
